how you make us three fall.

299
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:10,418
Xiaoyao is not your buddy.

300
00:17:12,019 --> 00:17:14,938
Though we are not buddies,
we are more than them.

301
00:17:15,499 --> 00:17:16,818
Come on, Xiaoyao.

302
00:17:18,458 --> 00:17:18,818
