00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:30,704
♪Why do I wish to hold your hand♪

532
00:35:30,704 --> 00:35:34,432
♪for the rest of my life♪

533
00:35:35,488 --> 00:35:37,632
♪Stay together forever♪

534
00:35:38,144 --> 00:35:40,771
♪Never to part♪

